item.title: CVE-2023-27318|2024-02-05T20:35:27.521Z -- netapp -- storagegrid%20%28formerly%20storagegrid%20webscale%29
item.description: StorageGRID (formerly StorageGRID Webscale) versions 11.6.0 through 11.6.0.13 are susceptible to a Denial of Service (DoS) vulnerability. A successful exploit could lead to a crash of the Local Distribution Router (LDR) service.
